walls from being damaged by chair backs.";i:35;s:199:"Today this chair rail molding is a fast way to stylishly define a dining room living room or entry hall especially when used to separate wallpaper from paint or between two different colors of paint.";i:36;s:113:"This design is built using a one-piece reed profile and 2 pieces of panel molding along the top and bottom edges.";i:37;s:86:"This is another wide elaborate chair rail suitable for large rooms with high ceilings.";i:38;s:128:"The nails are driven at the top of the arches in the profile to make filling the holes easier and less noticeable in the finish.";i:39;s:85:"Chair Rail Friezes Shop our collection of Chair Rail Moulding - Decorative Mouldings.";i:40;s:74:"Chair rail molding is a great way to add some dimensional style to a room.";i:41;s:75:"It has the added benefit of protecting the walls from damaging chair backs.";i:42;s:93:"If the walls are not protected then chairs will put dents and marks even holes in your walls.";i:43;s:97:"To keep your walls safe you can place a solid protective barrier or chair railing at about 36 to.";i:44;s:205:"A chair rail also known as a dado rail is a horizontal piece of trim that usually runs the perimeter of a room approx 36 from the floor but can also be awkwardly placed on a single wall popular in the 90s.";i:45;s:127:"When you have a chair rail it can be hard to figure out whether to use the SAME paint colour on the upper and lower portion of.";i:46;s:157:"Chair rail moulding is a decorative accent element that is applied to walls to provide scale and create a protective barrier against furniture wear and tear.";i:47;s:87:"It can come in a variety of materials including wood and medium-density fiberboard MDF.";i:48;s:64:"Chair rail moulding also comes in an array of shapes and styles.";i:49;s:82:"Ekena Millwork CHA03X01VI Victorian Casing Chair Rail 2 34H x 58P x 94 12L Primed.";i:50;s:18:"43 out of 5 stars.";i:51;s:148:"Stone Center Online Thassos White Marble 2